Welcome to the FORE Learning Hub!

FORE: Fundamentals of Robotics Education is an interactive learning website for those of a high school to undergraduate level with an interest in learning how to program robotics!

Embark on a fascinating journey into the world of robotics with our comprehensive learning resources. Whether you're a beginner or an enthusiast, our curated lessons and projects will guide you through the exciting realm of robotics programming.

Roadmap to Learning Robotics

  1. Introduction to Robotics

    Explore the basics of robotics, understanding its applications and significance in various industries.

  2. Programming with ROS

    Master the Robot Operating System (ROS) to program and control robots. Dive into hands-on lessons and practical examples.

    Experience a care-free environment to try your hand at programming in Python!

    Explore More

    Advanced Robotics Concepts

    Delve into advanced topics such as robot localization, mapping, and control algorithms to elevate your robotics skills.
